snippet.textDisplay: While I haven't had any ideas stolen, around Easter time last year, I drew up a design for an air turbine which would have effectively eliminated the need to recharge electric cars and made Elon Musk's electric car recharging stations obsolete. Unfortunately for me, When I checked the patent office website to see how to get it registered, I discovered that someone in South Australia beat me to it by submitting a design for an air turbine for electric cars in December the previous year.
